#~| "Usually &kmail; does this automatically, but under certain circumstances "
#~| "you might want to expire a folder manually.."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Deletes old messages from the current folder or moves them to another "
#~ "folder, according to the rules in the folder's <guilabel>Properties</"
#~ "guilabel> dialog (the default is not to delete or move old messages). "
#~ "Usually &kmail; does this automatically, but under certain circumstances "
#~ "you might want to expire a folder manually..."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Elimina as mensaxes antigas do cartafol actual ou móveas para outro "
#~ "cartafol seguindo as regras do diálogo <guilabel>Propiedades</guilabel> "
#~ "do cartafol (por omisión non se apagan ou moven as mensaxes vellas). "
#~ "Normalmente o &kmail; fai isto automaticamente, mais en certas "
#~ "circunstancias pode que vostede queira facer que o cartafol caduque "
#~ "manualmente."

