#~ "<guimenu>Cartafol</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agrupar as Mensaxes por Fíos e "
#~ "Asuntos</guimenuitem>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If enabled then the messages are not only grouped according to special "
#~ "information included in the messages but also according to their subject, "
#~ "&ie; messages with the same subject are considered as being related. If "
#~ "many messages are threaded below unrelated messages then you might want "
#~ "to disable this option."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Se isto estiver activo, as mensaxes agrúpanse non só de acordo coa "
#~ "información especial que se inclúe nas mensaxes mais tamén de acordo co "
#~ "seu asunto, &ie; considérase que as mensaxes co mesmo asunto están "
#~ "relacionadas. Se hai moitas mensaxes enfiadas por baixo de mensaxes sen "
#~ "relación, será mellor que desactive esta opción."

